import React, { Component } from 'react'; class ShippingCountryList extends Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.selectShippingCountryMenu = this.selectShippingCountryMenu.bind(this); this.state = { selected_shipping_country: 'Choose ...' } } selectShippingCountryMenu() { const countryMenu = document.querySelector('.shipping-country-menu'); const countryMenuOptions = document.querySelectorAll('.shipping-country-menu option'); countryMenu.classList.toggle('display-block'); for(let o=0; o < countryMenuOptions.length; o++) { countryMenuOptions[o].addEventListener('click', () => { this.setState({selected_shipping_country: countryMenuOptions[o].innerHTML}); this.props.country(countryMenuOptions[o].value); if(countryMenuOptions[o].value == 'US') { this.setState({state: true}); }else { this.setState({state: false}); } }) } } render() { return (
) } } export default ShippingCountryList
